.TH enc_source_continue_on_error  22.14 "Fri Oct 06 02:12:27 2023" 
.SH Name \fBenc_source_continue_on_error\fR
.SH Syntax \fBenc_source_continue_on_error\fR <value>
.P Type: Boolean
.P Default: false
.P Enables or disables source command to continue the script on tcl error. When set to true, the source command will ignore tcl errors and continue processing the script files. When set to false, a tcl error will halt the script. 
.SH Example
.P In the following example, the Tcl File (test.tcl) has an error i.e. no option specified after hyphen (-) for the setDesignMode command in the script.
.P test.tcl content:
.P ::::::::::::
.P puts "Testing Script for Errors"
.P setDesignMode -
.P puts "End Testing Script for errors"
.P ::::::::::::
.P If enc_source_continue_on_error is set to false, and setDesignMode is specified with hyphen only (without the option name after the hyphen), the script will end and will not source other commands mentioned after setDesignMode.
.P innovus 3> set enc_source_continue_on_error false
.P false
.P innovus 4> source test.tcl
.P Testing Script for Errors
.P Usage: setDesignMode [-help] [-reset] [-addPhysicalCell {hier|flat}] [-congEffort {low|medium|high|auto}] [-dual_rail_via_pitch <min_via_pitch> <min_filler_via_pitch> <cell_boundary_spacing>] [-earlyClockFlow {true|false}] [-expressRoute {true|false}] [-flowEffort {express|standard|extreme}] [-ignore_followpin_vias {true|false}] [-pessimisticMode {true|false}] [-powerEffort {none|low|high}] [-process <integer>] [-slackWeighting {unityWeighting|viewBasedWeighting}]
.P **ERROR: (IMPTCM-48):   ""-"" is not a legal option for command ""setDesignMode"". Either the current option or an option prior to it is not specified correctly.
.P If enc_source_continue_on_error is set to true,  and setDesignMode is specified with hyphen only (without the option name after the hyphen), the script will throw an error and continue to source the other commands without exiting.
.P innovus 5> set enc_source_continue_on_error true
.P true
.P innovus 6> source test.tcl
.P Testing Script for Errors
.P Usage: setDesignMode [-help] [-reset] [-addPhysicalCell {hier|flat}] [-congEffort {low|medium|high|auto}] [-dual_rail_via_pitch <min_via_pitch> <min_filler_via_pitch> <cell_boundary_spacing>] [-earlyClockFlow {true|false}] [-expressRoute {true|false}] [-flowEffort {express|standard|extreme}] [-ignore_followpin_vias {true|false}] [-pessimisticMode {true|false}] [-powerEffort {none|low|high}] [-process <integer>] [-slackWeighting {unityWeighting|viewBasedWeighting}]
.P **ERROR: (IMPTCM-48):   ""-"" is not a legal option for command ""setDesignMode"". Either the current option or an option prior to it is not specified correctly.
.P **ERROR: (IMPSE-110):   File 'test.tcl' line 2: errors out.
.P End Testing Script for errors 
.SH Related Information
.RS  "*" 2 source
.RE
.P
